name: The Same Purpose
description:
When viewed from the same side it will looked the same, although basically it's different from the big and small side, but the direction of all living things is the same, looking for light, light of life, light on the path to happiness.
⁣
It's not about who comes first, but how everyone can survive together.
⁣
An unbroken series of interconnected systems. One live then the other will live, one die then the other will die, will not be able to live alone.
